2/339432_mini.png?m=1547444004", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8df1/da52/339432_normal.png?m=1547444004", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/8df1/da52/339432_large.png?m=1547444004", "created": 1533694397, "last_modified": 1547444004}, "last_reply_by": "GuLuDaDuiZhang", "last_touched": 1719660654, "title": "V 友们，你们有痛风吗？一般多久好呢？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1053544", "created": 1719638925, "deleted": 0, "content": "## 2021 第一次痛风\r\n\r\n我在 2021 年的时候第一次痛风(右下脚大拇指关节)，那个时候尿酸好像有 500 多，痛了一个周，吃了几天秋水仙碱后环境，然后消肿，但是好了后似乎有点痛风结晶关节处肿\r\n\r\n## 2024 第二次痛风\r\n\r\n24 年开始就一直在吃苯溴马隆和碳酸氢钠片排泄尿酸，一直稳定在 200 ~ 350 ，6 月 14 号晚上慢跑了一小时步，第二天痛风就犯了，比较奇怪，这个时候尿酸不高。不过这一次痛了两周，现在脚还是肿的。目前在输液溶晶液，医生说不溶晶以后会更严重\r\n\r\n有痛友吗，你们现在情况怎么样了呢？可以分享下平时怎么管理自己的身体的吗。。。", "content_rendered": "<h2>2021 第一次痛风</h2>\n<p>我在 2021 年的时候第一次痛风(右下脚大拇指关节)，那个时候尿酸好像有 500 多，痛了一个周，吃了几天秋水仙碱后环境，然后消肿，但是好了后似乎有点痛风结晶关节处肿</p>\n<h2>2024 第二次痛风</h2>\n<p>24 年开始就一直在吃苯溴马隆和碳酸氢钠片排泄尿酸，一直稳定在 200 ~ 350 ，6 月 14 号晚上慢跑了一小时步，第二天痛风就犯了，比较奇怪，这个时候尿酸不高。不过这一次痛了两周，现在脚还是肿的。目前在输液溶晶液，医生说不溶晶以后会更严重</p>\n<p>有痛友吗，你们现在情况怎么样了呢？可以分享下平时怎么管理自己的身体的吗。。。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1719640441, "replies": 30, "id": 1053544}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 220404, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 4205, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 574121, "username": "bkzly83851", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/bkzly83851", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/704e9c390a1fabca19549f064092f711?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/704e9c390a1fabca19549f064092f711?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/704e9c390a1fabca19549f064092f711?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1646209463, "last_modified": 1686098746}, "last_reply_by": "leonshaw", "last_touched": 1719661172, "title": "关于三维立体画", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1053527", "created": 1719631661, "deleted": 0, "content": "小时候，大街上报亭买过这种画册，号称能在二维图片上看到三维的立体效果。出于好奇买过一本很重印刷质量很好，但死活看不出来有三维图像。\r\n刚刚突然想起有这种东西，上网一搜还真的有，例如： https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/585953406", "content_rendered": "<p>小时候，大街上报亭买过这种画册，号称能在二维图片上看到三维的立体效果。出于好奇买过一本很重印刷质量很好，但死活看不出来有三维图像。\n刚刚突然想起有这种东西，上网一搜还真的有，例如： <a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/585953406\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/585953406</a></p>\n", "last_modified": 1719631886, "replies": 28, "id": 1053527}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1691642161", "name": "bb", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1691642161", "title": "宽带症候群", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb", "topics": 15671, "footer": "", "header": "网速很重要。比快更快。", "title_alternative": "Broadband Symptom Complex", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1691642161", "stars": 7416, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 108, "parent_node_name": "geek"}, "member": {"id": 640177, "username": "vx007", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/vx007", "website": null, "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b88151202c35bd570493fd61b98a299e?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b88151202c35bd570493fd61b98a299e?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b88151202c35bd570493fd61b98a299e?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1690284033, "last_modified": 1690284033}, "last_reply_by": "vx007", "last_touched": 1719661558, "title": "代理规则中的 dns 不设置，也不会导致 dns 泄露！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1053566", "created": 1719649711, "deleted": 0, "content": "网上看了很多对 dns 泄露的讨论，为了防止 dns 泄露，很多人对 dns 模块进行了复杂的自定义设置。\r\n但我都是直接把配置文件中 dns 模块删除！只需在配置文件设置国内常用域名的白名单走直连，其他所有域名用 match 兜底走代理，ipcidr 和 geoip 规则全设置 no-resolve ，就不会有 dns 泄露。\r\n\r\n国内常用网站走国内 dns ，其他网站都在代理服务器端远程解析，这样既安全又不用配置 dns ，为什么不用？\r\n\r\n这样看来，那么多人都在追求的 dns 精细设置是否多此一举，有什么意义？", "content_rendered": "<p>网上看了很多对 dns 泄露的讨论，为了防止 dns 泄露，很多人对 dns 模块进行了复杂的自定义设置。\n但我都是直接把配置文件中 dns 模块删除！只需在配置文件设置国内常用域名的白名单走直连，其他所有域名用 match 兜底走代理，ipcidr 和 geoip 规则全设置 no-resolve ，就不会有 dns 泄露。</p>\n<p>国内常用网站走国内 dns ，其他网站都在代理服务器端远程解析，这样既安全又不用配置 dns ，为什么不用？</p>\n<p>这样看来，那么多人都在追求的 dns 精细设置是否多此一举，有什么意义？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1719650171, "replies": 28, "id": 1053566}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_large.png?m=1611920927", "name": "games", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_normal.png?m=1611920927", "title": "游戏", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/games", "topics": 2713, "footer": "", "header": "Life is short, have more fun.", "title_alternative": "Games", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_mini.png?m=1611920927", "stars": 2374, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 55, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 618154, "username": "enmail", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/enmail", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e16b2e8ea9266f1006246c96774d91f5?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e16b2e8ea9266f1006246c96774d91f5?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e16b2e8ea9266f1006246c96774d91f5?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1678413617, "last_modified": 1678413617}, "last_reply_by": "moonshing", "last_touched": 1719658394, "title": "B 站很多 UP 一百一百个抽黑神话悟空！", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1053498", "created": 1719619253, "deleted": 0, "content": "这是真抽假抽啊？游戏厂家会给补贴吗？\r\n这个抽 100 